      "title": "Environmental impacts of wild caught cod and farmed salmon-a comparison with chicken",
      "abstract": "Goal, Scope and Background ::: The objective of this study was to assess environmental impacts of Norwegian cod fishing and salmon farming and compare these with chicken farming in order to find reference levels for environmental performance and identify problem areas and potentials for improvements."
